  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK301">
<l>celliṭattuk kāppāṉ ciṉaṅkāppā ṉalliṭattuk</l>
<l>kākkileṉ kāvākkā leṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He restrains his anger who restrains it when it can injure; when it cannot injure, what does it matter whether he restrain it, or not ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
